OL,3,CSarah Mayhew: Man admits murder
OL,5,FA man has pleaded guilty to the murder
OL,6,Fof 38-year-old Sarah Mayhew whose
OL,7,Fremains were found in south London
OL,8,Fthis year.
OL,10,FBody parts belonging to Ms Mayhew were
OL,11,Ffound in Rowdown Fields in New
OL,12,FAddington, Croydon, on the 2nd of
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FAttending the Old Bailey on Thursday,
OL,16,FSteven Sansom admitted murdering Sarah
OL,17,FMayhew and perverting the course of
OL,18,Fjustice by dismembering her body,
OL,19,Fdisposing of it in various locations,
OL,20,Fand then cleaning up the crime scene.
